special_notes: Letter 'O' with Outer banks tags that start with OBX. OMIT all symbols. Example tags: NC-70A8DV (stacked DV keyed), NC-0LLAIC (stacked IC keyed), NC-OBX70975, NC-OBX99999 (first character is 'O'), NC-SC3A (prefix SC added), NC-2343NG, NC-NC3208 (vertical/small characters keyed). Stacked characters must be keyed.

stacked_character_rules.position: Y - OMIT vertical series title.; Y-Do NOT key verticals
